00:03:46.840 --> 00:03:50.160
in a way, although I've joined them in their world.

00:03:50.160 --> 00:03:52.600
They most probably think I lived in a different world,

00:03:52.600 --> 00:03:57.600
because I was brought up differently to them.

00:03:57.600 --> 00:04:01.560
I wanted Adele, my youngest, to go to university,

00:04:01.560 --> 00:04:02.560
and she did.

00:04:02.560 --> 00:04:04.920
She's got a really good job.

00:04:04.920 --> 00:04:06.520
But your mother wasn't like that.

00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:10.800
No, although my eldest daughter, Michelle,

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:14.160
she didn't want to go to university.

00:04:14.160 --> 00:04:16.040
She's done very well for herself,

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:18.920
and she's got a really good job as well.

00:04:18.920 --> 00:04:21.640
And I wanted one of them jobs, really,

00:04:21.640 --> 00:04:22.880
what them two have got.

00:04:22.880 --> 00:04:23.960
Right.

