I just turned up.

00:04:29.400 --> 00:04:32.800
I started work in 1964,

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:36.080
and when I started work,

00:04:36.080 --> 00:04:40.040
you could get one job in the morning,

00:04:40.040 --> 00:04:43.000
another one dinner time, if you didn't like that one,

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:44.800
maybe another one shortly after dinner,

00:04:44.800 --> 00:04:47.960
and a fourth one before the day was over.

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:50.280
It was booming.

00:04:50.280 --> 00:04:52.920
There was work there for everybody.

00:04:52.920 --> 00:04:54.760
You never heard of any many people

00:04:54.760 --> 00:04:57.160
who were actually on the dole, as it was.

00:04:57.160 --> 00:04:58.560
Right.

00:04:58.560 --> 00:05:00.360
